00:00:13.360 --> 00:00:16.540
Tolong ceritakan lebih banyak lagi tentang peramal di kafe.

00:00:16.920 --> 00:00:19.000
Saya mendapat pertanyaan seperti itu,

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:22.080
